title: Dow Analyst Moves: DOW - Nasdaq.com
text: The latest tally of analyst opinions from the major brokerage houses shows that among the 30 stocks making up the Dow Jones Industrial Average, Dow is the #23 analyst pick. Within the broader S&P 500, when components were ranked in terms of analyst favorites, DOW claims the #350 spot.    makeArticleAd();  Looking at the stock price movement year to date, Dow is lower by about 6.3%.
